Package: Cyclones
Title: Recreate tropical cyclone conditions.
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Benjamin", "Branoff", , "benjamin.branoff@usda.gov", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Cyclones fetches and assembles data corresponding to tropical cyclone disturbance forces. 
    Initital conditions are limited to wind, precipitation, and storm surge but future versions may be more inclusive. Any previous storm on record and
    in the IBTrACS dataset can be produced, as well as any hypothetical storm using the same data format. Methods, data sources, and final 
    product resolutions are all adjustable. Winds can be modeled when native data are sparse and final wind products can be compared against
    available drop sonde measurements from hurricane hunter reconnaisance missions. Parallel operations are possible both internally and 
    externally.
